General.Name: OX2 AB
General.GicIndustry: Independent Power and Renewable Electricity Producers
General.Description: OX2 AB (publ) develops and sells wind farms and solar parks. It operates in Sweden, Finland, France, Italy, Lithuania, Norway, Poland, Romania, Estonia, Åland, and Spain. The company was formerly known as OX2 Wind AB and changed its name to OX2 AB (publ) in February 2019. The company was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden. OX2 AB (publ) is a subsidiary of Xygen Bidco AB.
